review: From wanting to be a parent, to a happy mother today, I am always comfortable in consulting the doctor. review: we visited  so many hospitals  ,but she is very friendly, after so many years of marriage  when we lost all our Hope of having children Dr.tejaswini mam has done parenthood  dreams of infertile couples come true.we met her immediately and after thorough examination  of us she started our treatment and we are blessed  with a baby girl and expenses  are also very reasonable. couples who have infertility  problems  definitely meet her she makes your dream  come true.The treatment was on time as required we recommend this doctor  to all.

review: I heard about the doctor from a family friend of ours... I am so glad that I came to know about her and visited her for  my  pregnancy and  am now blessed with healthy baby girl after 3 miscarriages with gestational diabetes. The most distinguished feature about her is that she is most focused on her treatment with  good out comes on high risk pregnancies.  I would strongly recommend her. Thank you madam for all your efforts and patience.
